Reasoning: The paper focuses on a vision-language task of grounding referring expressions in images, which involves both computer vision and natural language processing. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a novel method that involves Bayesian modeling and deep learning, which falls under the sub-categories of cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper addresses the problem of complex context modeling, which is related to the sub-category of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper evaluates its method on various benchmarks, which is relevant to the sub-category of cs.MM (Multimedia).
